room_title: Escape room "The Hurricane Room" by Escape House Waterville in Orange Beach
room_address: 906 Gulf Shores Pkwy. Gulf Shores, AL 36542
room_description: A hurricane is coming your way. Your team only has 60 minutes to find a shelter where you can be safe. To open the shelter you and your team need to find all the clues and puzzles, and you need to find out the details about the hurricane. If you succeed, you will be safe at last. You can't avoid the catastrophe, you can only hide away from it.
